OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Shelf-stacking pays more  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fthan caring for people'    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, There are fears residential homes could
OL,6, close and patients put at risk without 
OL,7, more care workers, according to those  
OL,8, working in the sector.                 
OL,10,FAnd pay is a reason some believe       
OL,11,Fthere's a lack of care workers, while  
OL,12,Fthe Welsh government pledged to provide
OL,13,Fmoney for staff to get the real living 
OL,14,Fwage of #9.90 an hour in April.        
OL,16,FIt has since jumped 10%, but it is not 
OL,17,Fyet clear if it could find more cash.  
OL,19,FOne home boss has recruited overseas,  
OL,20,Fsaying locals can earn more in shops.  
